# ⚠️ `newton-physics` has been renamed to `newton`

This package (`newton-physics`) has been **renamed**.
The actively maintained package is now published as **[`newton`](https://pypi.org/project/newton/)**.

## What to do

Replace `newton-physics` with `newton` in your dependencies:

    pip install newton

If you previously depended on `newton-physics`, update your `requirements.txt` or
`pyproject.toml` to depend on `newton` instead.

